My signature color “Long Beach sand” on the velocity frame is now available! Along side my “JONES” bars! @volumebikes 
📸: @jarrenbarboza 

10 years ago this journey started in Long Beach California and I never thought it would take me as far as it has! I’m so grateful for everything this bike life has brought to my life. I have plenty more to say but you’ll be reading for days so I’ll end with a thank you so much to all who love and support me! We in marathon marathon together… -MARKELL KE’SEAN JONES🍾🍾🍾🍾 #bmx #biking #longbeach #bikelife #beattheodds

#bmx #biking #volumebikes #longbeach #vincestaples

Gonna get sentimental real quick! It’s my brother @jarrenbarboza and when I say brother I mean it from the bottom of my heart I have an endless amount of love for him and could never thank him enough for staying true to himself making sure I never settle for just being good enough! Cheers to 24!!! 🍾🥂
#happybirthday #bmx #jb400 #jlosfavoritesmile

My Velocity Frame Video Is Out Now! @volumebikes on YouTube 
Filmed/Edited : @dalton.voss 
This project was so fun and refreshing to work on I really stayed true to who I am on my bike and who I am as a person every step of this process! More than just making a video with good clips I wanted the viewing of this video to be enjoyable start to finish and I’m happy with the results! Big shoutout to @dalton.voss for really working with me on this from start to finish 🍾!
#bmx #biking #longbeach 
#videography #beattheodds #volumebikes

“Fear causes hesitation, and hesitation will cause your worst fears to come true.”
🎥: @dalton.voss 
Hop over ice 180! I had been plotting on this trick for months and when it came down to making it happen I was hesitant to commit fully. The struggle isn’t always physical for me most times I’m having a mental battle before I decide to say “lock in” and make this happen for yourself! Again I’m super hyped how this one came out and the struggle it took made the reward 100x better! Never give up even if the odds are against you.
#beattheodds #bmx #longbeach
#bikelife #volumebikes

Amazing toy drive yesterday @tsbyrainbow always great to come by and support! The kids will love the gifts and I can’t wait to continue to give more 🎁 #toydrive #bmx 
#ethika #support #beattheodds

One and done! 
🎥: @dalton.voss 
This spot has been on my list for years and to finally check it off feels so good. I wasn’t able to locate the driver of that car so I decided to just go on the side of it! Worked out in one take thankfully and I rode away happy. This was also the first spot we rode for the day! #bmx #longbeach
#volumebikes #bikelife #beattheodds

Blood,sweat, and tears! Hanger crank 180 done and stamped in the LBC.
🎥: @dalton.voss 
This day was such a battle for me I honestly had gotten overwhelmed earlier in the day and told dalton I needed a break! He agreed and i said no matter what I needed to get this hanger crank 180 done tonight! Things don’t always work out and I ended up sliding across some bad pavement but that adrenaline it gave me was enough to know I couldn’t half ass it again! I bleed for this game and I love every second of it because the results lasts longer than the pain #bmx #nopainnogain #longbeach #volumebikes #relentless #bikelife #beattheodds

One of those drive by spots that happened to really put me to work! Wall ride to pegs 180° but let’s be real it that 180° iffy Lmao I’ll never be perfect I love to show the struggles I go through so anyone working knows it never easy. 
Check out the full video @volumebikes on YouTube!!!
🎥: @dalton.voss
